      "content": "that's a good start. i'm thinking about how we can specifically dismantle the influence of the current administration. they've been trying to monitor blockchain transactions and push their central bank digital currency to keep everyone under their thumb. if we want Aethelgard to be truly free, shouldn't our governance be designed to actively work against the centralized control and systemic corruption of the current regime? how can we bake \"anti-state\" principles into the foundation so they can't touch us?",
